Name: Basic Platformer
About the game: Its a basic platformer, where you have to run through three levels of progressively getting harder. Their are two types of enemies you will encounter, the first being a slime and the second being a fly. To defeat both you simply have to jump on top of them, then there's the spike traps. As it stands there are three levels, I intend to make more levels to the game in the future.
